      "text": "そ、そうなのね。千紗らしいとは思うけど\n確かにちょっと、尖り過ぎかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… It’s so like you‚ Chisa‚ but\nBut it might be a bit too unconventional.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.5666631064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 222.3833508654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
