      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうかなぁ？　みんなにも受け入れてもらえるように\n4怖ぐらいで抑えるつもりだったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I was planning to keep it\naround a level 4 on the scary scale so people could still enjoy it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.5666834515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.2569788142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
