      "text": "尖ってるだけじゃなくて、怖い曲でもあるのね……\nでも、千紗らしい案だし、別の機会に使えるといいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it’s not just unconventional—it’s scary too…\nBut it’s very like you. Maybe you can use it another time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.9000167848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.6699262146
    },
    {
