      "text": "うん。{user}さんにもそう伝えてみる\nお姉ちゃんはどんなテーマにしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I’ll tell {user}-san that too.\nWhat theme did you choose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.3000167848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.0056631252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
